reviews.text:
Usually good. But ticket office is often closed when it should be open!! Needed season ticket urgently!

Update: Amended review to 4 stars. Noticed the ticket office has been opened regularly very early. Great to see!!
Lovely little quaint station. Make sure your in the right carriage if arriving as short platforms. Ticket office not open all day. Two sheltered areas platform one and one platform two

Four stars for the station, it may be old, but it's still useable. The loss of the star is not the station however accounting for Southern Rail who are almost never on time and cancelled trains a lot.
A small railway station on the scenic Arun Valley Railway.
Great little Southern Railway station, with quaint archetecture, and a super friendly Station Master named Mark, who is always there to give fantastic travelling information.
